{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101700,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_game_0002_01","textHome":"店里卖的都是战斗少女的必需品，@欢迎光临调整屋商店～"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":101700,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":101700}]}],"group_10":[{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":101700,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_game_0002_10","textHome":"黄昏……以及夜幕降临时，魔法少女@就会开始行动……为了不让大家受伤，@我也得好好努力一把。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"id":101700,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101700,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"id":101700,"motion":300}]}],"group_11":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":101700,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_game_0002_11","textHome":"大家都能够平安无事地再到店里来吗……@呵呵，对不起。一到晚上我就会@变得有点多愁善感。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":101700}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101700,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":101700}]}],"group_12":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_051.exp.json","id":101700,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_game_0002_12","textHome":"有时候大家会问我“你在开玩笑吗？”，@但我是认真的哦？我是认真地@在逗你们嘛，呵呵。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":101700,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101700,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":101700}]}],"group_2":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101700,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_game_0002_02","textHome":"出战的准备都做好了吗？本调整专家@会为大家送上安心与安全哦。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"id":101700,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":101700,"motion":100}]}],"group_3":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":101700,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_game_0002_03","textHome":"欢迎光临，想让我调整一下灵魂宝石吗？@哎呀，这次你是来买东西的啊。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.8,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101700}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_051.exp.json","id":101700,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.2,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101700}]}],"group_4":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101700,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_game_0002_04","textHome":"这里的道具全都蕴藏着我的真心哦。来，@告诉我你想买什么吧。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":101700,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.2,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101700,"motion":200}]}],"group_5":[{"autoTurnFirst":6.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101700,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_game_0002_05","textHome":"为了感谢大家平日里的光顾，调整屋@正在开展期间限定的促销活动哦♪"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":101700,"motion":100}]}],"group_6":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101700,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_game_0002_06","textHome":"现在是商店丰收的季节。过了这村@就没这店了，所以一定要好好逛逛哦？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":101700,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":101700,"motion":300}]}],"group_7":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101700,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_game_0002_07","textHome":"哎呀，被你发现啦，你这贪心鬼。呵呵，@看看货架就知道啦。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":101700,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":101700}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101700,"motion":1}]}],"group_8":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":101700,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_game_0002_08","textHome":"“２４小时营业”只是句宣传语啦……@我最怕早起了，所以就让我多睡会儿吧…@还是说，你就这么想让我陪陪你？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":101700,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101700,"motion":200}]}],"group_9":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101700,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_game_0002_09","textHome":"白天店里也很闲，是最悠闲的时候啦。@呵呵，你方便的话，我们一起@去吃个午饭吧。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":101700}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101700,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":101700}]}]},"version":3}